{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Multiple CNN-based feature extractors were trained using different labeled datasets to allow the selection of the most suitable feature extractors for the target data.",
    "In addition, an unsupervised approach to learn the plankton image features based on the momentum contrast method (He et al. 2020) was proposed.",
    "The idea is to use data augmentation to generate two different instances of the same image and use a loss function that forces the model to learn similar feature representations for both instances.",
    "Moreover, two custom clustering methods were proposed: (1) shrunken k-Means, and",
    "(2) Partially Labeled k-Means."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "In addition, an unsupervised approach to learn the plankton image features based on the momentum contrast method (He et al. 2020) was proposed."
  ]
}